{"tid":1474284,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一篇勸世文，勇武同和理非入黎望下","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:17:39.000Z","uid":304806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1add9d86c1d1e56a186621e169e7dc1e2a4acbb","tid":1474284,"uid":304806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"嗱，少少諗法，勸世文，我無春袋唔岩錫嘴好la，屌都麻煩細力d唔該。<br />\n<br />\n分化呢個技能對家一早練到Lv.max嫁la，但係佢地有幾樣野，好值得我地學習，唔好精神潔癖住，取長補短係上策呀。<br />\n<br />\n1.分工明顯<br />\n<br />\n無論popo或者建制做左幾多人神共憤ga野都好，佢地ga冷氣軍師同鍵盤戰士總可以第一時間文宣美化佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">簡單地講，你地儘管出去做野，做錯我地諗計幫你兜！</span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野係可以杜絕到分化，因為大大減少左大家ga磨擦，主動執屎同被動食屎個心態好大分別嫁，而前線做野ga時候又可以有彈性d，why not?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n嗱，我地有內鬼，對家都有，但點解我地d鬼傳訊息出黎都起唔到大作用呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單，對家係利用內鬼，我地係捉內鬼，就好似機場單野咁，我地收到ga訊息係對家利用內鬼放ga,好多素人或者和理非就被屌為散水撚(包括我，大佬我錯),進而被分化。<br />\n<br />\n就算無中計都會擔心安全，尤其係老人家同父母，然後我地再集會就gg左，right？<br />\n<br />\n如果當時捉到個公安，叫齊記者影住我地拍手歡迎佢，呢d就叫利用鬼la。<br />\n<br />\n3.兵不厭詐<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野大家開始醒覺嫁la,大佬而家風頭火勢咩招都要出，我地要ga係勝利唔係道德高地，咩唔想變到同對家一樣。<br />\n<br />\n呀，以真服人呀，嗱，我欣賞加了解，問題係，尺度自己衡量ga啫，好似「支持還警察一個清白，支持成立獨立調查委員會」呢d Lv，一D問題都冇嗱？冇抹黑冇扭曲事實la?咁，點解唔詐？講事實大家ok la？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得，衝衝子要人ga時候，和理非總在身後;和理非要保護ga時候，衝衝子永遠在前。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">岩聽唔岩聽都好，最重要一點！核爆都唔割呀！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：P牌仔幫fd子po文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e632c0878651a31be9412a3388b0cabcd9bee901","tid":1474284,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:25:25.000Z","msg":"推！斬狗首不割"},{"pid":"9eca9755564966a9d9bc14a42c2165cb650a9cf6","tid":1474284,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"時事台好快沉 你要自己推下文先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421001f6532a20dccf313d01dd4a37153a50261e","tid":1474284,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68186075ceba3db306717522344d2bf75dd34495","tid":1474284,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"推到有人幫手做文宣<br />\n<br />\n[事先通知] 8．18民陣完場全民入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65be97dd79f76ee146ca5d29d010cc7bb0c72cbb","tid":1474284,"uid":304806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37920dce85bb34489622dc22be0ffb90a5dc6d9","tid":1474284,"uid":304806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02f2df7c8378c6623fdce21472d05a561bf457b8","tid":1474284,"uid":304806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d65432ce294bff57d6e366f1df6f7c88d650845","tid":1474284,"uid":304806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:58:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9414c31fdd37c5f7a7ce119454cbdc6ecba1fef6","tid":1474284,"uid":280183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cc880eaad8a5f13e718fd4f77b95a7e32dc332","tid":1474284,"uid":193401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n樓主係有point嘅<br />\n大家目標一樣<br />\n諗下點樣利益最大化仲好啦"},{"pid":"073f1e9d1ca223c242e868ade7086301655d380a","tid":1474284,"uid":304806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.